Currently, Portfolio allows to create multiple issue links for an epic, i.e., it suggests if an epic spans multiple projects, to create multiple issues and link all of them, one link PER jira project. 

In many instances, epics exist only once, in one selected JIRA project, since story-epic links can be cross-project. Thus, there is a need when creating and linking issues, to establish the epic link in JIRA also if stories and epics are in different projects.

